    All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DistributedJoin.DJInputFormatArray.DJRecordReader, DistributedJoin.DJInputFormatRTree.DJRecordReader

    public abstract class BinaryRecordReader<K extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.mapred.RecordReader<PairWritable<K>,PairWritable<V>>
    Reads every possible pair of values from two underlying record readers. In other words, it makes a Cartesian product from the records stored in the two splits given to this reader.
    Author:
    eldawy
